name: Lolita Locket
description:
This necklace features a beautiful cameo profile of a lolita skeleton goddess colored in ivory on a black resin background and is securely set in an antique silver plated locket with a stunning scroll design. The pendant hangs from a fine antique silver plated chain which measures 18" (46cm) in length and closes with a lobster claw clasp. The cameo measures approximately 40 x 30mm, and the setting is 2 1/2" long. The locket opens, and inside may hold up to 2 pictures.

Choose your option if you'd prefer your locket with a rose, or no rose.
